reviewText: The Connie Francis Scrapbook-An American Treasure features the story of Connie's life and career. With much video commentary by Connie Francis, this is the real deal. She has been my favorite singer for years ever since I bought her Looking For Love album. Conniw Francis fans, and lovers of star biographies will like it the most. Highly recommended.
video did cover the highlights of connie francis's career. All in all pretty good video.
